## Corewar ##

Initialisation:
	Init new fresh memory VM
	Handle argv in coreware initiation
		Handle options
		Check syntax
			Check conflicts
	Handle champions
		Parse champions
			IF not enough data (prog missing / too large) return error
			ELSE put champion at the right place in VM
